metadata.description:
ZanozaRare membership pass :

You have only one chance to submit your collector profile, think two time before selling your pass.

Drops gonna be in limited editions, dropped randoms or raffled and if you hold some specials sets, you can receive free rewards, many ideas to try, this is an experiment.
